title: NZ Fitness - May 2014
description:
NZ Fitness - May 2014

72 Pages | True PDF | English | 16 MB 


NZ Fitness is New Zealand's leading fitness magazine. Over the past 25 years the magazine [incorporating Fitness Life], has built up a strong following among those interested in keeping fit, healthy and motivated.  The full colour glossy magazine has a list of eminent highly regarded writers with sections on Performance, Nutrition, Healthy Food, Fitness Trends, Exercises, Mens Muscles and Weekend Getaways. In each issue we will run features on highly successful people who have made fitness an integral part of their life - and by reading their story you will feel highly motivated too.
